#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:team_sports_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For annual contributions, you can easily manage specific prices for each "
"team by setting up pricelists. Once this is set up in the Teams app, you can"
" select all the players to whom you want to send the contribution request. A"
" smart button, <em>Request Contribution</em>, will appear. Click it to "
"select the correct product, assign a tag corresponding to the period, and "
"generate all the Sales Orders."
msgstr ""
